    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: C++17, GNU make, CMake (>= 3.16), Flashlight Text (https://github.com/flashlight/text/), KenLM Text (https://github.com/kpu/kenlm/), Boost (libboost-dev libboost-program-options-dev libboost-system-dev libboost-thread-dev libboost-test-dev)
